was recently discovered in southern Xiqi.

141
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:04,000
In half a month,

142
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:05,560
I will return to Mocheng

143
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:06,840
with the Young Master of Xiqi

144
00:08:06,840 --> 00:08:08,040
and the dowry.

145
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:13,960
