242
00:12:54,880 --> 00:12:56,520
the osmanthus mung-bean cakes
she usually eats.

243
00:12:56,520 --> 00:12:58,240
These are all new recipes I've made.

244
00:12:58,240 --> 00:12:59,040
When she returns,

245
00:12:59,040 --> 00:13:00,770
I want her to try something new.

246
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:05,760
How much longer are you going to
busy yourself

247
00:13:05,760 --> 00:13:07,290
with these useless things?

248
00:13:08,040 --> 00:13:09,570
The Queen's trip this time…

249
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:10,720
